{"tid":340601,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老冇屋住 goodest logic","createTime":"2017-07-30T05:48:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-30T06:01:41.000Z","uid":100251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a7fef2a005a7e6b3faa1fd8d908aaf002fc4b351","tid":340601,"uid":100251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:48:20.000Z","msg":"頭先落去放狗散步<br />\n我一向都唔放繩<br />\n行到攰見到有長椅就坐下，隻狗一直係地下<br />\n突然有個戴帽老伯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 走黎好大聲咁問我識唔識字<br />\n係咁大聲鬧話唔可以帶狗黎<br />\n我好聲好氣同佢講，明明告示寫左「基於公共衛生理由，狗隻不得站坐於椅上」<br />\n佢話佢唔識字，咁我諗住算，唔計較<br />\n點知佢仲鬧得大聲d，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話「就係你地d人養畜生，扣晒分，搞到我地d老人冇屋住」<br />\n嘩，goodest logic<br />\n之後又爆粗又話要報警又話要拉我坐六個月<br />\n<br />\n廢老無敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf12484c67a87888a3e23d1ff7be883397030ea","tid":340601,"uid":104613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:51:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b9ac00a2e006a5aabfe272e4436a0eb78a90ee09","tid":340601,"uid":100251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:55:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你搭佢搏頭話你係幫乜乜官放狗<br />\n問佢係咪想死</blockquote><br />\n佢幾好笑架，話你識字，你最叻，你老豆做律師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實依家大部分人都識d字<br />\n唔知佢係咪穿越左時空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2db16301430b49f24a24f04832ee87a7c7e102f5","tid":340601,"uid":619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T05:55:57.000Z","msg":"幫佢報埋警啦"},{"pid":"c551ee2ca2593cdaa377076dc4d324abdfb498f3","tid":340601,"uid":100251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-30T06:01:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幫佢報埋警啦</blockquote><br />\n一陣d人以為我恰佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}